<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #222; background-color:
      #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 30px; } .container { background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); max-width:
      500px; margin: auto; padding: 32px; } .brand { color: #0a6cf1;
      font-weight: bold; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 8px; } .otp {
      font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #0a6cf1; margin: 24px 0; }
      .note { color: #e67e22; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="brand">Kharon Pay</div>
      <h2>Verify Your Account</h2>
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>We're excited to have you on board! To complete your sign-in, please
        use the One-Time Password (OTP) below:</p>
      <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
      <div class="note"><b>Note:</b>
        This code will expire in 15 minutes for your security.</div>
      <p>If you did not request this code, please ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br />The Kharon Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>